snippet.title: ZombiU - Gamescom Trailer [UK]
snippet.description:
Visit the official Website: http://www.zombiu.com
Join us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/zombiugame/
Only the prepared will survive. Download the mobile app : https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/zombiu/id574425152?mt=8


For the second time in history, a great plague has enveloped London in a fog of death. Big Ben tolls as hundreds upon thousands of the unprepared die or are infected by a sickness worse than death.

You are still breathing, for now. But how long will you survive..."
